类 WordEntry

java.lang.Object
appDomain.WordEntry
所有已实现的接口:
Serializable, Comparable<WordEntry>
public class WordEntry extends Object implements Comparable<WordEntry>, Serializable
The WordEntry class represents a word entry in the system, tracking its occurrences across multiple files and lines. Each WordEntry includes the word in lowercase form, along with a list of file locations where the word was found.

This class implements the Comparable interface to allow sorting by the word value. It also provides methods for adding locations, generating reports, and retrieving metadata about the tracked word.
